skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sully's steamers
des:
Sully's Steamers Greenville provides a limited sampling of all the deli options available. To use, say "Alexa, open Sully's Steamers." You can hear about the menu items by saying, "Hey Sully, what's on the menu?"
If you need directions you can say "Help." The application also provides store hours as well as information about ordering for offices and catering.
